name: But beautiful
description:
She told me that he might forget how to smile as his childhood.
He had disorder.
And then she told me as she smiled, "But look, I cannot say something more since I still believe he would smile again same like before. He's beautiful. how can I stop saying love you babe to him?"
Yes. I still remember that moments were beautiful as if it never exist before.
